Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.71,0:23:03.84,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1377711,1383841}{\blur3}It is lonely by myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.84,0:23:09.93,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1383841,1389931}{\blur3}…and I almost stumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.93,0:23:21.94,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1389931,1401941}{\blur3}Somewhere calls me here,\Njust like a whisper in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.94,0:23:34.08,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1401941,1414081}{\blur3}Purple light, shining down\Non the horizon…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.08,0:23:39.96,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1414081,1419961}{\blur3}…more surer than words…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:46.09,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1419961,1426091}{\blur3}…telling us gently…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.09,0:23:52.18,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1426091,1432181}{\blur3}…that we'll meet\Neach other someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.18,0:23:58.27,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1432181,1438271}{\blur3}Of course you can\Nfly from far away…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.27,0:24:04.28,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1438271,1444281}{\blur3}…for the dream\Non my cheek…
